structure.unit: A AUTOMATED MOTOR VEHICLE REGISTRATION SYSTEM

law.history: Repealed 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 128, sec. 14, effective July 15, 1998; amended 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 128, sec. 6, effective July 15, 1998. -- Created 1982 Ky. Acts ch. 164, sec. 32, effective July 15, 1982.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Form of certificate of title issued by department.
metadata.lrc-note: (7/15/98). Under KRS 446.260, the repeal of this section in 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 128, sec. 14, prevails over its amendment in 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 128, sec. 6.
